Description:
    Add breaking changes from an existing OpenAPI changeset to existing OpenAPI descriptions

Example:
    bin/rails generate openapi_breaking_change \
      --changeset-path app/api/description/changesets/202204000000_remove_rate_limit_rate.yaml \
      --description-path app/api/description/components/schemas/rate-limit.yaml

    This will modify `app/api/description/components/schemas/rate-limit.yaml` to include `x-github-breaking-changes` referencing the `remove_rate_limit_rate` changeset.  The developer will then need to fill in the OpenAPI patch section
